name: Unidentified_armored_male
content:
A Human male was on the Dibrook Space Station, where he watched the reporter Cianba on the HoloNet when the space station was attacked by Yuuzhan Vong Yorik-Vec starships. The attack tore a hole in the space station and the man was blown out into space.
The human wore a brown shirt, with a blue, bulky breastplate and armor covering his body. He was armed with various weapons, including a dagger.
